Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, Orochimaru's going\Nto take your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If it happens, it happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a kid, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge is everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can carry out my revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it's no concern of mine\Nwhat happens to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Put simply, neither I nor Orochimaru\Ncan defeat Itachi right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I can obtain the power\Nto accomplish that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,by giving my body to Orochimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll give him as much of\Nthis life of mine as he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:16.13,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(803,598)}Title\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The talking's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto and Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to do anything rough\Nin front of you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm going to get serious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, serious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just let those
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,who left the village in the same way\Nas Orochimaru run loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll do whatever I have to do\Nto haul Sasuke back to the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hidden Leaf, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother with that Jutsu, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to\NLord Orochimaru like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no reason to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what the Akatsuki\Nare up to, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We want these guys from\Nthe Hidden Leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to take care of the Akatsuki for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As many of them as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your revenge won't turn out well
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,if the other Akatsuki\Nget in the way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pathetic reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It should increase your chances of revenge,\Neven if only by one percent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once again...I couldn't stop him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm...totally weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying won't bring Sasuke back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here! I'll get stronger with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got...\Nclose to six months left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes without saying that three\Nare better than two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm pretty strong myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is just the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto and the others fought Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But, their original mission was to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, their mission was to capture\Nthe spy Sasori sent to Orochimaru
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring him back to the Hidden Leaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and to get information about Orochimaru\Nand Sasuke as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sasori's spy, Kabuto Yakushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,already had Sasori's Jutsu\Nbroken by Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems Orochimaru tried to use\Nthis opportunity to kill Sasori,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,not knowing that the real Sasori\Nwas already dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto made contact with Orochimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,became unable to\Ncontrol his emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and ran amuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto eventually\Nreleased his fourth tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and went wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru did battle\Nwith the Nine-Tails Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even he probably reached his limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stabilize\N\N\N\N\NIt seems he tried to disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,while Yamato was attempting\Nto control Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Yamato's clone secretly\Npursued Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, they found Orochimaru's hideout\Nand made their way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it seems they encountered Sasuke\Nand a battle ensued.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So...then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Sasuke has become\Nsignificantly more powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear Naruto didn't stand\Na chance against him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't get so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears Naruto wasn't able\Nto show his full power
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,because of damage from\Nthe Nine-Tails Cloak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm not all that depressed,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured Sasuke would be stronger\Nat this point in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Naruto will be more fired up\Nfor future training
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,after having realized the difference\Nbetween Sasuke and himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we should be happy\Nthey made it back safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fortunate that Naruto\Nwas able to make it back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However, although unexpected situations\Nare an inevitable part of missions...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought he would end up\Ndoing battle with Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And here, it's best to keep Naruto\Nin the village
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because things like this\Nend up happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that hard-head\Nwould depart from his opinions so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I will issue\Nyour next mission immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand by at home until I contact you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakura.\NLet's go on a date together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten what Lady Tsunade\Nsaid just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What'd she say again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to stand by at home
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,until Team Kakashi's next mission\Nhas been determined, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? She won't find out if\Nwe just go out for a little while!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go by yourself\Nif you want to go out on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to\Ngo on a date by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what about Sai's activity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You were right\Nto be concerned, Lady Tsunade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Danzo gave him a special mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A special mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Sai was put in charge\Nof undercover work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,dealing with potential risks\Nto the Hidden Leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,while carrying out his mission as
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,an Anbu Black Ops member\Nunder Danzo's direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai's purpose for joining us in\NTeam Kakashi was to bury Sasuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who is to become the new vessel\Nfor Orochimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the individual of most concern\Nto the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured he was a crafty guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As would be expected of the leader\Nof a hard-line military faction,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,his actions are strong-armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But our protective feelings\Nfor the Hidden Leaf are the same, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Danzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then could you hold off on\Nyour conclusions until you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Danzo gave this to Sai as\Na gift for Orochimaru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in order for the contact with Orochimaru\Nto proceed smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a list of Anbu Black Ops members!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! That jerk, Danzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did he get the list from\N{\i1}the classified files...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...Lady Tsunade...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizune! Tighten security at\Nthe classified files storehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and change the deciphering codes\Nfor the files. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! That sly old dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always the crafty one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time when the outside\Nof the village
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is in an uproar with Orochimaru\Nand the Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd have to be concerned\Nabout trouble {\i1}inside{\i0}  the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll be forced to consider Sai's\Nearlier proposal with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd fail\Nthe special mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very unlike you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A favor, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:17:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you keep me in Team Kakashi\Nunder this name for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That smile on his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already taken that up\Nwith Tsunade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you understand that emotions\Ncreate hate, don't you, Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And hate creates battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bonds of hatred with\N{\i1}my older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the person who acknowledged\N{\i1}me more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a special bond\N{\i1}I was finally able to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrade
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you know\N{\i1}what the word comrade is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course, I do.\N{\i1}What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a meeting about\Nour next mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I'm coming.
